"2016-12-01T02:13:06.000Z","msg":"今年暑假去咗歐洲8國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b7bb82c3341dd9abfa1d15166c203d336c4c97","tid":15004,"uid":11198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"我12月就去北歐<br />\nPlan左少少咁<br />\n反而可以留幾耐好似無咩人講<br />\n香港免簽現家歐盟180天內只可最長留90天<br />\n同你講唔出行程/無離開歐盟嘅證明<br />\n佢有權唔比你入（應該同難民問題有關）<br />\n因為我同樓主一樣想玩耐d<br />\n搵搵下先發現呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我本身想去到先plan變現家要plan<br />\n<br />\n利申：問過一位專帶歐洲旅行團嘅導遊講我知<br />\n申請visa就唔清楚，如有錯巴打屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我反而想問下北歐嘅巴打係咪唔洗換咁多現金<br />\n信用卡都夠做"},{"pid":"c866cdbb75553c8e105e516887fc3729f178e111","tid":15004,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"去過英德法奧匈捷克波蘭比利時荷蘭 加土耳其<br />\n咁算唔算環歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a084b12c428bd902df94026ff610cbd63dc3c225","tid":15004,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:28:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去左東歐十五國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄去咗幾多日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個月左右"},{"pid":"f4accba08b9d00d4fd0430c06ed73d55c3590eff","tid":15004,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"極光、太自然去北歐；古代中古歷史文化西歐中歐；冷戰共產去東歐；陽火海灘南歐。斷斷續續去左兩個月。"},{"pid":"b09d546686d39f16c9ac55d0954ddd1185fe6796","tid":15004,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"現代文明發源地去一世都睇唔完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9248a86450000f2af76e49a2a1064a6ea0209b05","tid":15004,"uid":34424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"