br />\n西歐北歐同信用卡都方便<br />\n但北歐有時自助簽卡畀錢要pin"},{"pid":"02bffdc28620fdead8dac19522133f2c85e0e0f3","tid":15004,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"東歐抵玩 波蘭捷克匈牙利<br />\n<br />\n另外我d朋友之前會出一出歐盟 好似就可以？我唔肯定 因為我有visa"},{"pid":"93e085bb4b424fafcac4677422db8e8170d64446","tid":15004,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"嗰陣去左瑞典波蘭捷克 丹麥西班牙葡萄牙 比利時荷蘭 匈牙利 挪威冰島英國保加利亞希臘 極光我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知再講"},{"pid":"895f7393afada3f46f7cd7a387086b0ac1b6d0ef","tid":15004,"uid":21997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去左東歐十五國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師兄去咗幾多日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個月左右</blockquote><br />\n邊個國家你覺得最正?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n推介保加利亞 馬其頓 科索沃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f288a5441973f2ddad2840eed232670610b2a066","tid":15004,"uid":11198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰陣去左瑞典波蘭捷克 丹麥西班牙葡萄牙 比利時荷蘭 匈牙利 挪威冰島英國保加利亞希臘 極光我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上網睇唔申請visa 得90日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該丹麥-挪威-法羅群島-冰島-挪威北部<br />\n用太多錢就直落東/南歐，唔再玩北歐<br />\n細佬我都係想追極光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打分享下挪威心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbfc44c4e213dcd00442d6a4de44f9156b2a2f3","tid":15004,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嗰陣去左瑞典波蘭捷克 丹麥西班牙葡萄牙 比利時荷蘭 匈牙利 挪威冰島英國保加利亞希臘 極光我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上網睇唔申請visa 得90日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該丹麥-挪威-法羅群島-冰島-挪威北部<br />\n用太多錢就直落東/南歐，唔再玩北歐<br />\n細佬我都係想追極光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打分享下挪威心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我買左冰島機票既關係<br />\n挪威其實淨係玩得3日<br />\noslo同bergen<br />\noslo好現代化 可能因為我嗰陣已經係北歐留左一段時間 我覺得麻麻地oslo 可以去睇下民俗博物館<br />\nbergen就超級靚 童話小鎮咁"},{"pid":"8e4f4246623c66d590b1246b1adf8153031e4f50","tid":15004,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"最後睇定堆歷史去，否則你好易審美疲勞，唔知度度有咩分別"},{"pid":"909b29c4511a91756e0db453b4b04806768c6392","tid":15004,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>嗰陣去左瑞典波蘭捷克 丹麥西班牙葡萄牙 比利時荷蘭 匈牙利 挪威冰島英國保加利亞希臘 極光我都有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上網睇唔申請visa 得90日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該丹麥-挪威-法羅群島-冰島-挪威北部<br />\n用太多錢就直落東/南歐，唔再玩北歐<br />\n細佬我都係想追極光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打分享下挪威心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我買左冰島機票既關係<br />\n挪威其實淨係玩得3日<br />\noslo同bergen<br />\no